{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We want to let people know, or whoever survived, that we have survived because different people survived under such different circumstances.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody knew the whereabouts of another person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started traveling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started traveling out of Busko, going in the direction of our hometown, Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we thought-- we will-- we knew we cannot stay in Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew our house was nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know if anybody could make a life there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we got-- after a long, long, treacherous journey, by all modes of transportation-- by foot, by wagon, by-- partly by train-- we reached Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, as I previously mentioned, we, of course, went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Loszek and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Loszek to thank them for actually saving our lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We contacted Henryk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thanked him for saving our lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We told the Loszeks that we are going to get all the papers-- my, my parents own real estate in Lodz and Radomsko-- that we are going to get all the real-estate papers in order and transfer all of the holdings to them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we went to that person whom our parents entrusted all the silver, and all the furs, who told us he had never received it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did give me a pillowcase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How would he have thought that I would not have known that something was contained in that pillowcase?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the pillowcase has my mother's monogram because this was her trousseau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had all her linens monogrammed in her monogram.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the pillowcase got so stained and yellowed-- it was pure linen-- that what I did, I cut just the monogram to be framed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was nobody in Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't find any Jews in Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
